{{Japanese|japanese= 野村 哲也|kana= のむら てつや|romaji= Nomura Tetsuya}}

'''野村哲也'''（{{bd|1970年|10月8日}}）是[[日本|日本]][[游戏制作|游戏制作]]公司[[史克威尔艾尼克斯|史克威尔艾尼克斯]]（原[[史克威尔|史克威尔]]）的[[游戏总监|游戏总监]]及[[角色设计师|角色设计师]]。其最早曾在游戏《[[最终幻想V|最终幻想V]]》以及《[[最终幻想VI|最终幻想VI]]》项目中参与工作，自《最终幻想VII》起开始进行游戏的角色设计工作，并曾为多部游戏做角色设定。另外野村哲也还担任过2002年开始发行的系列游戏[[王国之心|王国之心]]的制作监督，并执导[[CGI|CGI]]电影《[[最终幻想VII_降临之子|最终幻想VII 降临之子]]》。<!-- is a Japanese video game director and character designer working for [[Square_Enix|Square Enix]] (formerly [[Square|Square]]). He first started work designing [[Final_Fantasy_V|Final Fantasy V]] and [[Final_Fantasy_VI|Final Fantasy VI]] and has also been the character designer of various games, debuting in [[Final_Fantasy_VII|Final Fantasy VII]]. Additionally, Nomura debuted as video game director for the [[Kingdom_Hearts|Kingdom Hearts]] series starting in 2002 and was also the director for the CGI film [[Final_Fantasy_VII_Advent_Children|Final Fantasy VII Advent Children]]. --><ref>{{cite web |author=Next Generation staff |title=The Hot 100 Game Developers of 2007 |work=Next Generation |publisher=[[Future_Publishing_USA|Future Publishing USA]] |date=2007-03-03 |language=en |7= |accessdate=2013-10-30 |url=http://www.next-gen.biz/features/hot-100-game-developers-2007 |archive-date=2012-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120820032431/http://www.next-gen.biz/features/hot-100-game-developers-2007 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

野村哲也因其在《[[王国之心_(游戏)|王国之心]]》中的贡献而和[[桥本真司|桥本真司]]一同获得{{tsl|en|International Game Developers Association||国际游戏开发者协会}}授予的“杰出视觉艺术奖”<!-- Nomura received the "Excellence in Visual Arts" award by the {{tsl|en|International Game Developers Association}} for his work in the [[first_Kingdom_Hearts_game|first Kingdom Hearts game]], alongside Shinji Hashimoto. --><ref name="KHgamerankings">{{cite web| url = http://ps2.ign.com/articles/388/388484p1.html| title = IGDA Names Metroid Game of the Year| publisher = [[IGN|IGN]]| date = March 7, 2003| accessdate = 2013-10-30| archive-date = 2010-12-16| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101216204056/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/388/388484p1.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>。在[[IGN|IGN]]的“史上最佳100名电子游戏制作人”（The Top 100 Video Game Creators of all Time）中，野村哲也获列第84位<!-- In [[IGN|IGN]]'s "The Top 100 Video Game Creators of all Time" Nomura was listed at number 84. --><ref name="ign">{{cite web | author = Perry, Douglass C. | url = http://uk.games.ign.com/top-100-game-creators/84.html | publisher = IGN | title = 84. Tetsuya Nomura | language = en | accessdate = 2013-10-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131031085709/http://uk.games.ign.com/top-100-game-creators/84.html | archivedate = 2013-10-31 }}</ref>。

== 早年 ==

野村哲也出生在日本[[高知县|高知县]]。18岁从{{tsl|ja|高知県立岡豊高等学校||高知县立冈丰高等学校}}毕业后就[[上京|前往东京]]，进入设计专业学校学习[[广告设计|广告设计]]。毕业后于1991年4月16日进入史克威尔公司。<ref name="dream183">『[[ニンテンドードリーム|ニンテンドードリーム]]』 2009年7月号 Vol.183「キャラかみ」第5回 インタビュー。</ref><!-- Nomura was born in [[Kōchi|Kōchi]], Japan. He graduated from vocational school with a degree in [[graphic_design|graphic design]]. -->

== 职业生涯 ==

=== 1990年代 ===

在20世纪90年代初，野村受雇于史克威尔公司并担任《[[最终幻想IV|最终幻想IV]]》项目的调试员，之后他又担任了《[[最终幻想V|最终幻想V]]》的怪物设计师，以及《最终幻想VI》的图形总监和怪物设计。<!-- In the early 1990s, Square hired him to work as a debugger for [[Final_Fantasy_IV|Final Fantasy IV]] and following it as a monster designer for [[Final_Fantasy_V|Final Fantasy V]] and then as the graphic director in charge of monster designs for [[Final_Fantasy_VI|Final Fantasy VI]]. --><ref name="ign" />

1995年，野村哲也迎来了他最为著名的一项工作，当时史克威爾准备为[[SFC|SFC-CD系统]]推出《最终幻想》系列最新作，项目总监[[坂口博信|坂口博信]]和野村哲也一起对原来的小说进行了修改，后[[索尼|索尼]]与[[任天堂|任天堂]]因关系恶化致使SFC-CD系统计划搁浅，導致野村等人的开发计划也暂告一段落。
两年后，当史克威爾参與索尼[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]平台的方向已經明朗化后，《[[最终幻想VII|最终幻想VII]]》的开发计划正式提上了议事日程。坂口博信本人一直对原先的剧本抱有难以割舍的感情，于是指派[[北濑佳范|北濑佳范]]和[[野岛一成|野岛一成]]两人进行了再创作，而史克威尔公司指示原作者野村哲也替代[[天野喜孝|天野喜孝]]，担任《最终幻想VII》的[[角色设定师|最终幻想VII的角色设计师]]<!-- 
Nomura's most notable work came in 1995, when Square asked him to be the {{tsl|en|Character design of Final Fantasy|character designer}} for [[Final_Fantasy_VII|Final Fantasy VII]] to replace [[Yoshitaka_Amano|Yoshitaka Amano]]. --><ref name="FlareG">{{cite web| author=Knight, Sheila| year=2003| title=Tetsuya Nomura 20s| url=http://flaregamer.com/b2article.php?p=81&more=1| publisher=FLAREgamer| language=en| accessdate=2013-10-30| archive-date=2013-04-20| archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20130420015300/http://flaregamer.com/b2article.php?p=81&more=1| dead-url=no}}</ref>。野村表示因受平台机能以及游戏质量、题材等的限制，天野狂放飘逸的画风在硬件条件局限的情况下，无法以[[三维计算机图形|3D]][[计算机图形学|计算机图形]]技术忠实再现，而野村哲也平实的写实风格的人物设定比较适合《最终幻想VII》项目的3D化，而且更容易获得新生代玩家的支持<!-- Nomura has expressed that Final Fantasy VII was hindered by graphical limitations, and as such his designs were very plain in comparison to his real style. --><ref name="Hist of FF7">{{Cite web|url=http://retro.ign.com/articles/870/870770p1.html|title=IGN Presents: The History of Final Fantasy VII|publisher=IGN|first=Rus|last=McLaughlin|date=April 30, 2008|language=en|accessdate=2013-10-30|archive-date=2012-01-23|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/64tTUHLXN?url=http://retro.ign.com/articles/870/870770p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他亦参与多处游戏玩法和情节的制作<!-- He also took part in the making of various parts from the gameplay and plot. --><ref name="ign" />，使得他的名字逐漸有了知名度。1997年，他回归最终幻想系列参与了《[[最终幻想VIII|最终幻想VIII]]》的人物设定工作，本作在商业上取得了巨大的成功。1998年他参与游戏《[[寄生前夜_(游戏)|寄生前夜]]》和《[[Brave_Fencer_Musashi|武藏传]]》的制作。应游戏监制北濑佳范的要求，野村与艺术总监[[Yusuke_Naora|直良有佑]]合作将游戏人物制作的更为逼真<!-- It was a critical and commercial success. In 1998, he worked on both [[Parasite_Eve|Parasite Eve]] and {{tsl|en|Brave Fencer Musashi}}. In 1997, Nomura worked on [[Final_Fantasy_VIII|Final Fantasy VIII]], a game that achieved commercial success, where he returned as the character designer. Nomura worked alongside art director {{tsl|en|Yusuke Naora}} in making characters more realistic, an approach requested by director [[Yoshinori_Kitase|Yoshinori Kitase]]. --><ref name="development">{{cite web |title=Interview with Nomura, Kitase and Naora |url=http://playstationjapan.tripod.com/ff8iview2.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001104316/http://andriasang.com/comxpx/ffxiii_2_character_designers/ |archivedate=2012-10-01 |date=1998-06-05 |work=[[Shūkan_Famitsu|Shūkan Famitsu]] |publisher=[[ASCII_Corporation|ASCII Corporation]] |language=en |accessdate=2013-10-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。此外，他也是负责设计游戏战斗序列的战斗视觉总监<!-- Additionally, he was the battle visual director, in charge of designing sequences from the game's fight. --><ref name="ign" />。<!-- Afterwards, Nomura worked on several other different projects for Square (now Square Enix), as a character designer in {{tsl|en|Ehrgeiz}} for the PlayStation which also used characters from Final Fantasy VII in 1998. -->

=== 2000年代 ===

在2001年，回归最终幻想系列并为《[[最终幻想X|最终幻想X]]》设定人物之前，野村为[[beat_'em_up|beat 'em up]]游戏《{{tsl|en|The Bouncer||保镖}}》做角色设定工作。<!-- During 2001 he was the character designer for the [[beat_'em_up|beat 'em up]] {{tsl|en|The Bouncer}} before returning to character designing for the [[Final_Fantasy|Final Fantasy]] series with [[Final_Fantasy_X|Final Fantasy X]] in 2001. -->野村还协助制作人员，使[[Full_motion_video|全动态影像]]中的角色衣着与游戏部分中的一致，而不是像《最终幻想VIII》中那样有较大差异<!-- Nomura also worked with the staff so that characters' clothes would be identical in {{tsl|en|Full motion video|full motion scenes}} and in-game parts unlike in Final Fantasy VIII, --><ref name="FlareG" />。在2000年2月，他开始了游戏《[[王国之心_(游戏)|王国之心]]》的监制工作，项目制作团队来自史克威尔公司和[[迪士尼互動|迪士尼互動工作室]]，两家游戏制作公司计百余名成员<!-- During February 2000, he started working as the director for the development of [[Kingdom_Hearts|Kingdom Hearts]] with the production team consisting of over one hundred members from both Square and {{tsl|en|Disney Interactive}}. --><ref>{{cite web| url = http://ffx.sakura.ne.jp/kh.htm| title = Kingdom Hearts キングダム ハーツ| publisher = Final Fantasy 2000| language = ja| accessdate = 2013-10-30| archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/64xK1Yyq2?url=http://ffx.sakura.ne.jp/kh.htm| archive-date = 2012-01-25| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。在桥本真司与坂口博信就在游戏中使用动画《[[米老鼠|米老鼠]]》角色的一次讨论中，野村首次的得知了该游戏项目。野村从任天堂公司出品游戏《[[超级马里奥64|超级马里奥64]]》中获得了《王国之心》的制作灵感。在同迪斯尼的工作人员讨论过后，野村说服他们在游戏中使用原创角色，同时野村本人也亲自担纲角色设定<!-- Nomura first heard of the game during a discussion between [[Shinji_Hashimoto|Shinji Hashimoto]] and [[Hironobu_Sakaguchi|Hironobu Sakaguchi]] regarding the use of the character of [[Mickey_Mouse|Mickey Mouse]] in a video game. Nomura was inspired to work in Kingdom Hearts by [[Nintendo|Nintendo]]'s video game [[Super_Mario_64|Super Mario 64]]. After discussing with the Disney staff, Nomura convinced them to use original characters with Nomura also working as the character designer. --><ref>{{cite web| url = http://andriasang.com/con0h5/kh3d_iwata_asks/| archiveurl = https://archive.is/20120803203547/http://andriasang.com/con0h5/kh3d_iwata_asks/| title = Iwata Asks Tetsuya Nomura About Kingdom Hearts 3D| publisher = Andriasang| archivedate = 2012-08-03| date = April 3, 2012| language = en| accessdate = 2013-10-30| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。本作男主角[[索拉_(王国之心)|索拉]]也成为了当时野村最喜爱的角色<!-- The game's protagonist, [[Sora|Sora]], became Nomura's favorite character he designed so far. --><ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.kh2.co.uk/website/interviews/opm|title = Kingdom Hearts II: Nomura Press Conference (OPM)|publisher = Kingdom Hearts Ultimania|date = 2010-03-18|author = |language = en|accessdate = 2013-10-29|archive-date = 2020-11-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112012730/http://www.kh2.co.uk/website/interviews/opm|dead-url = no}}</ref>。继《王国之心》的开发后，野村再度回到最终幻想系列，并参与《[[最终幻想XI|最终幻想XI]]》和《[[最终幻想X-2|最终幻想X-2]]》等多部游戏的制作。<!-- Following Kingdom Hearts, Nomura worked once again in the Final Fantasy series including [[Final_Fantasy_XI|Final Fantasy XI]] and [[Final_Fantasy_X-2|Final Fantasy X-2]]. -->

当史克威尔艾尼克斯公司以1997年PlayStation游戏《最终幻想VII》背景为故事[[wikt:蓝本|蓝本]]，开展“[[最终幻想VII补完计划|最终幻想VII补完计划]]”[[跨媒体制作|跨媒体制作]]项目时，野村哲也再次成为角色设计师。<!-- For the [[Compilation_of_Final_Fantasy_VII|Compilation of Final Fantasy VII]] [[metaseries|metaseries]] which featured new titles based on Final Fantasy VII, Nomura was once again the character designer. Various returning characters were recreated due to their lack of appearances in Final Fantasy VII as well as to be similar to other recurring characters they are related. --><ref name="completeguide">{{cite book |title=Dirge of Cerberus Official Complete Guide|year=2006 |isbn=978-4-7575-1622-9 |language = ja | publisher=Square-Enix |pages=}}</ref>。计划的首部作品《[[危机之前_-最终幻想VII-|危机之前 -最终幻想VII-]]》于2004年发售。<!-- He first worked in [[Before_Crisis:_Final_Fantasy_VII|Before Crisis: Final Fantasy VII]] released during 2004. -->

《王国之心》的续集，国际版游戏《[[王国之心Final_Mix|王国之心Final Mix]]》，新增了更多关于系列的情节伏笔<!-- A sequel to Kingdom Hearts started development around the completion of [[Kingdom_Hearts_Final_Mix|Kingdom Hearts Final Mix]], an international version which added more foreshadowing elements regarding the series' plot. --><ref name="GS-NI-Dengeki">{{cite web| url = http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/rpg/kingdomhearts2/news.html?sid=6076646| author = GameSpot Staff| publisher = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]| date = 2003-10-10| title = Kingdom Hearts II's Tetsuya Nomura Q & A| language = en| accessdate = 2013-10-30| archive-date = 2012-01-31| archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6576ajhuU?url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/kingdom-hearts-iis-tetsuya-nomura-q-and-a-6076646| dead-url = no}}</ref>。2004年，野村带领制作团队完成了[[Game_Boy_Advance|Game Boy Advance]]平台游戏《[[王国之心_记忆之链|王国之心 记忆之链]]》。野村原本打算直接继续在PlayStation 2平台上制作续作《[[王国之心II|王国之心II]]》，但应玩家们渴望在掌上游戏机平台上游玩到系列原生作品的诉求，制作团队制作了《记忆之链》来填补《王国之心》与《王国之心II》之间的空白<!-- Nomura continued his worked in the [[Kingdom_Hearts|Kingdom Hearts]] series with [[Kingdom_Hearts:_Chain_of_Memories|Kingdom Hearts: Chain of Memories]] for the Game Boy Advance in 2004. Nomura originally planned to directly work in the PlayStation 2 sequel [[Kingdom_Hearts_II|Kingdom Hearts II]]. However, desire from fans to play the original game in a portable console resulted in the creation of Chain of Memories which would bridge the gap between Kingdom Hearts and Kingdom Hearts II. --><ref name="KHCoM-NI1">{{cite book| title = Kingdom Hearts [[Ultimania|Ultimania]]: Revised Edition| year = 2002| language = ja| publisher = Studio BentStuff| isbn = 4-7575-1349-6}}</ref>。

在接到北濑佳范的电话邀请之后，野村也参与了“最终幻想VII补完计划”的制作。在计划中他执导了[[计算机图形界面|CGI]]动画影片《[[最终幻想VII_降临之子|最终幻想VII 降临之子]]》，本片于2005年在日本发行，2006年4月25日在北美发售，同时他亦为片中的原声音乐创作歌词。本片也是野村的电影处女作，为此他重新设计了剧中人物<!-- He also directed the CGI animated film [[Final_Fantasy_VII_Advent_Children|Final Fantasy VII Advent Children]] which was released on 2005 in Japan and in North America on April 25, 2006, and also wrote some of the lyrics that appear on the soundtrack. This was also Nomura's film debut, and he re-designed the characters as well. Nomura joined the Square crew after producer Yoshinori Kitase called him. --><ref name="gspot">{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/08/13/square-enix-announces-official-final-fantasy-vii-advent-children-complete-art-gallery|title=Square Enix Announces Official Final Fantasy VII Advent Children Complete Art Gallery|author=IGN Staff|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=August 13, 2010|language=en|accessdate=2013-10-30|archive-date=2019-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503033944/https://www.ign.com/articles/2010/08/13/square-enix-announces-official-final-fantasy-vii-advent-children-complete-art-gallery|dead-url=no}}</ref>。野村之所以会同意加入并执导计划，在很大程度上还是源自他对于《最终幻想VII》中角色[[Cloud_Strife|Cloud Strife]]的依恋<!-- Nomura agreed to direct the project, largely in part because of his attachment to the character of [[Cloud_Strife|Cloud Strife]]. --><ref name="twointerview">{{cite web| title = Interivew with Kazushige Nojima and Tetsuya Nomura from FLAREgamer.| url = http://flaregamer.com/b2article.php?p=109&more=1| publisher=FLAREgamer| date = October 10, 2005|language=en | accessdate =2013-10-30}}</ref>。他与野末武志共同担当导演一职<!-- He split the role of directing with Takeshi Nozue. --><ref name="prologue">{{cite book |title=Final Fantasy VII Advent Children Prologue |year=2005 |isbn=4-08-779339-7 |language = ja | publisher=Square-Enix |pages=}}</ref>。2009年4月16日，史克威尔在原片的基础上增加了部分新片段，并以[[导演剪辑版|导演剪辑版]]再次发行<!-- On April 16, 2009, Square released a [[director's_cut|director's cut]] of the film which added new content to original film. --><ref name="newcontent">{{cite web| url = http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-03-27/my-chemical-romance-founder-co-produces-ffvii/acc-song| title = My Chemical Romance Founder Co-Produces FFVII: ACC Song| publisher = Anime News Network| date = March 27, 2009| language = en| accessdate = 2013-10-30| archive-date = 2009-09-19| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090919155412/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-03-27/my-chemical-romance-founder-co-produces-ffvii/acc-song| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

《王国之心II》之后于2005年发行，本作解释了首部游戏神秘结尾中的一些伏笔。<!-- Kingdom Hearts II was later released in 2005 resolving the elements foreshadowed in the first game's secret ending. -->作为以前作之后一年为背景的游戏，野村细致的设计了将游戏情节，使其也能让初次接触系列的玩家理解<!-- As a result of being set a year after previous titles, Nomura was careful to make the plot accessible to newcomers. --><ref>{{cite book |title=キングダムハーツII アルティマニア |trans_title=Kingdom Hearts II Ultimania |year=2005|isbn=978-4-7575-1621-2 |language = ja | publisher=Square Enix |pages=}}</ref>。在史克威尔艾尼克斯完成了《王国之心II》升级版《王国之心II Final Mix+》的开发工作之后，迪斯尼制作方与系列游戏制作人野村接洽，表示对游戏续作的制作很感兴趣。野村表示，“（对于新作）我们有各种各样的想法，但目前还未到可以公开的时机”。<!-- After Square Enix finished development of the updated versionKingdom Hearts II Final Mix+, Kingdom Hearts producer Nomura was approached by Disney who expressed interest in a sequel. Nomura said "We have various ideas, but we're not at the point where we can say that." --><ref>{{cite web |author=Anoop Gantayat |url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/742/742527p1.html |title=Nomura on Kingdom Hearts III - PS2 News at IGN |publisher=IGN |date=2006-10-30 |language=en |accessdate=2013-10-30 |archive-date=2013-06-12 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HKWjtj3c?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/10/30/nomura-on-kingdom-hearts-iii |dead-url=yes }}</ref>野村希望暂时不再以[[索拉_(王国之心)|索拉]]为主角，而是通过其他人物的视角来继续该系列游戏<!-- Wishing to stop using the character of Sora temporarily, Nomura instead wished to continue the series with games that explained different subplots. -->。这一构想最终成为了游戏《[[王国之心_358/2天|王国之心 358/2天]]》，本作于2008年在任天堂DS平台上发售，故事背景设置在《王国之心II》的情节之前<!-- This resulted in the creation of [[Kingdom_Hearts_358/2_Days|Kingdom Hearts 358/2 Days]] for the Nintendo DS in 2008 which explored events that set the story of Kingdom Hearts II. --><ref name="ScenarioMysteries">{{cite book |title=キングダムハーツII FINAL MIX+ アルティマニア |year=2007 |isbn=978-4-7575-2013-4|language = ja | publisher=Square-Enix |pages=}}</ref>。在2007年年中，野村谈及希望在移动手机平台上制作一部王国之心系列的衍生作品，并希望其玩起来与系列中其他作品略有所不同。这就是背景被设定在《王国之心II》之后的《[[王国之心_编码|王国之心 编码]]》，本作2010年重制为《王国之心 编码重制版》在任天堂DS平台发售<!-- In mid-2007, Nomura mentioned a desire to create a spin-off Kingdom Hearts game on a mobile platform and wanted it to play slightly different than other titles in the series. The resulted was [[Kingdom_Hearts_coded|Kingdom Hearts coded]], a game set after the events of Kingdom Hearts II, which was later remade for the Nintendo DS in 2010. --><ref name="JS-PortableKH">{{cite web| title = Next Kingdom Hearts to be portable spin-off, not KHIII| url = http://www.joystiq.com/2007/05/04/next-kingdom-hearts-to-be-portable-spin-off-not-khiii/| author = Ransom-Wiley, James| date = 2007-05-04| publisher = Joystiq| language = en| accessdate = 2013-10-30| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131031094649/http://www.joystiq.com/2007/05/04/next-kingdom-hearts-to-be-portable-spin-off-not-khiii/| archive-date = 2013-10-31| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

在此期间，他还负责完成任天堂DS平台游戏《[[美丽新世界_(游戏)|美丽新世界]]》的设计和编排。他也是2009年游戏《[[最终幻想XIII|最终幻想XIII]]》的主要角色设计师。因 PlayStation 3以及Xbox 360比前代游戏主机更出色的图形处理能力，使得野村在进行角色设定时可以使用比过去更多的复杂元素，例如[[雷光_(最终幻想)|雷光]]的披风和详细的面部特征。同时的这意味着，图形制作团队不得不在每一个角色或者区域上，做出比以往游戏制作过程中更多的工作。野村在[[非玩家角色|非玩家角色]]的创建中却并不采用复杂的手法<!-- In the meantime he was also responsible for the complete designing and orchestration of [[The_World_Ends_with_You|The World Ends with You]] for the Nintendo DS. In 2009, he was also the main character designer of [[Final_Fantasy_XIII|Final Fantasy XIII]]. The graphics capabilities of the PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360 compared to previous consoles allowed Nomura to use more complex elements in the character designs than before, such as Lightning's cape and detailed facial features. This in turn meant that the art team had to do much more work for each character or area than in previous games. Nomura did not take an involved role in the creation of the [[non-playable_characters|non-playable characters]]. --><ref name="SUCHARint">{{cite book |title=Final Fantasy XIII Scenario Ultimania |publisher=Studio Bentstuff |location=Tokyo |isbn=4-7575-2775-6 |pages=50–52 |language = ja |date=2010-02-01}}</ref>。2008年，他为游戏《[[最终幻想_纷争|最终幻想 纷争]]》做角色设定。<!-- In 2008, he was the character designer of [[Dissidia_Final_Fantasy|Dissidia Final Fantasy]] -->野村最初所设想的《最终幻想 纷争》是一部由迪斯尼动画角色担纲主角的王国之心衍生作。之后野村觉得迪斯尼人物之间若要互相争斗感觉不舒服，而最终选择使用最终幻想系列中的人物<!-- Dissidia Final Fantasy was originally envisioned by director Nomura as a Kingdom Hearts spin-off featuring a cast of Disney characters. Nomura later felt uncomfortable with the Disney characters fighting each other and instead opted to use Final Fantasy characters. --><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2009/06/30/dissidia-final-fantasy-originated-from-kingdom-hearts Dissidia: Final Fantasy Originated From Kingdom Hearts|title=Dissidia: Final Fantasy Originated From Kingdom Hearts|author=Ishaan|publisher=Siliconera|date=2009-06-30|language=en|accessdate=2013-10-24|archive-date=2019-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504134938/https://www.siliconera.com/2009/06/30/dissidia-final-fantasy-originated-from-kingdom-hearts/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。野村亲自负责游戏中角色的设定，人物与天野喜孝原作插画中的造型和风格相比有很大变化<!-- Nomura was responsible for the character designs, which changed much of the look and style of Yoshitaka Amano's illustrations. --><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ffworld.com/?rub=news&page=voir&id=758 |title=Dissidia : Images et informations ! |accessdate=2013-10-30 |author=KujaFFman |date=2007-05-09 |work=[http://www.ffworld.com/ Final Fantasy World] |publisher= |language=fr |archive-date=2007-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070512005908/http://www.ffworld.com/?rub=news&page=voir&id=758 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/6170645.html |title=Final Fantasy XIII, Dissidia rock Square Enix Party |accessdate=2013-10-30 |author=GameSpot Staff |language=en |date=2007-05-12 |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |publisher=[[CNET_Networks|CNET Networks]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070514085702/http://www.gamespot.com/news/6170645.html |archivedate=2007-05-14 }}</ref>。

=== 2010年代 ===

2010年，史克威尔发布了首作《王国之心》的前传《[[王国之心_梦中降生|王国之心 梦中降生]]》，并且解构了《王国之心II》以及其后升级版本中的某些场景和情节<!-- During 2010, Square released [[Kingdom_Hearts_Birth_By_Sleep|Kingdom Hearts Birth By Sleep]], a prequel of the first Kingdom Hearts that explained scenes shown in Kingdom Hearts II and its updated version. --><ref name="ScenarioMysteries" />。在2011年春，史克威尔发售了《最终幻想 纷争》的后续作品《[[最终幻想_纷争012|最终幻想 纷争012]]》。本作很大程度上展现出了野村在开发制作初期的许多设想和理念，包括新加入的角色和游戏机制<!-- In early 2011 Square released a follow up to Dissidia titled [[Dissidia_012_Final_Fantasy|Dissidia 012 Final Fantasy]]. The game carried several ideas Nomura had ever since early development such as the inclusion of new characters and new gameplay mechanics. --><ref name="system">{{cite web|url=http://thelifestream.net/news/general-final-fantasy-news/6575/dissidia-final-fantasy-duodecim-012-tetsuya-nomura-interview/|title=Dissidia Final Fantasy Duodecim 012 Tetsuya Nomura Interview and More|publisher=The Lifestream|author=Makoeyes987|date=September 16, 2010|language=en|accessdate=2013-10-30|archive-date=2016-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160327150636/http://thelifestream.net/news/general-final-fantasy-news/6575/dissidia-final-fantasy-duodecim-012-tetsuya-nomura-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。及至2011年的《[[最终幻想XIII-2|最终幻想XIII-2]]》时，野村仅负责创建了人物的面部，而角色服装设计交由其他制作人员<!-- For the 2011's [[Final_Fantasy_XIII-2|Final Fantasy XIII-2]], Nomura only created the characters' faces as other members the staff designed their clothes. --><ref name="naora">{{cite web|title=Final Fantasy XIII-2's Serah, Noel and Moogle Detailed by Character Designers|url=http://andriasang.com/comxpx/ffxiii_2_character_designers/|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121001104316/http://andriasang.com/comxpx/ffxiii_2_character_designers/|archivedate=2012-10-01|publisher=Andriasang|language=en|accessdate=2013-10-30|date=August 24, 2011|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。当《王国之心 编码重制版》发布时，野村和他的开发伙伴们就已经开始考虑《[[王国之心_3D_［梦降深处］|王国之心 3D ［梦降深处］]]》的开发和发行，游戏背景设定在《[[王国之心III|王国之心III]]》故事前。出于开发团队对主机品质的积极评价，本作发布于[[任天堂3DS|任天堂3DS]]平台上<!-- Once the Kingdom Hearts coded remake was released, Nomura and his companions already had thought to release [[Kingdom_Hearts_3D:_Dream_Drop_Distance|Kingdom Hearts 3D: Dream Drop Distance]], a game that would set the events of [[Kingdom_Hearts_III|Kingdom Hearts III]]. The game was released for the Nintendo 3DS owing to the team's positive reaction to the console's quality. --><ref name="nintendopowerinter">{{cite journal|journal=Nintendo Power|publisher=Nintendo of America|pages=40–41|title=Kingdom Builder|issn=1041-9551|issue=276|date=March 2012}}</ref><ref name="igntalk">{{cite web|url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/113/1135182p1.html|title=Tetsuya Nomura Talks Kingdom Hearts 3DS|author=Anoop Gantayat|date=November 17, 2010|work=|publisher=IGN|language=en|accessdate=2013-10-30|archive-date=2011-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713005025/http://ds.ign.com/articles/113/1135182p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。野村证实，为了纪念系列发行十周年以及吸引新玩家的加入，他将考虑引进所谓的“高清技术测试”（HD Technical Test）<!-- Nomura confirmed that he would be considering what he called a "HD Technical Test" in order to commemorate the series' tenth anniversary and to entice players new to the series. --><ref name="andriasang">{{cite web|url=http://gonintendo.com/?mode=viewstory&id=168616/|title=Kingdom Hearts: Dream Drop Distance - release date revealed|publisher=GoNintendo|date=December 11, 2011|language=en|accessdate=2013-10-30|archive-date=2019-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502183617/https://gonintendo.com/?mode=viewstory&id=168616%2F|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2012年3月3日首发仪式活动上，作为游戏发售庆祝，其现场展示包含全CGI制作的游戏序章的游戏片段<!-- This occurred on March 3, 2012 in the form of a premiere event where footage from the game, including its full CGI introduction sequence, was showcased to celebrate the game's release. --><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2012-03-23/kingdom-hearts-3d-game-premiere-light-show-streamed|title=Kingdom Hearts 3D Game's Premiere Light Show Streamed|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=March 23, 2012|language=en|accessdate=2013-10-30|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520040624/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2012-03-23/kingdom-hearts-3d-game-premiere-light-show-streamed|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在2012年5月，野村透露将在游戏《[[最终幻想_Versus_XIII|最终幻想 Versus XIII]]》以及一款待公布王国之心游戏中担任监制<!-- During May 2012, Nomura revealed he was still working as the director of [[Final_Fantasy_Versus_XIII|Final Fantasy Versus XIII]] as well as a new Kingdom Hearts game that has yet to be announced by Square Enix. --><ref>{{cite web|title=INTERVIEW: Tetsuya Nomura|url=http://www.next-gen.biz/features/interview-tetsuya-nomura|publisher=[[Edge_Online|Edge Online]]|language=en|accessdate=2013-10-30|author=Edge Staff|date=25 June 2007}}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.girlgamersuk.com/2012/05/nomura-expects-new-kingdom-hearts-announcement-soon/|title=Tetsuya Nomura Expects New Kingdom Hearts Announcement Soon|author=TurtleGirl|date=May 1, 2012|work=|publisher=girlgamers|language=en|accessdate=2013-10-29|archive-date=2019-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502040548/http://www.girlgamersuk.com/2012/05/nomura-expects-new-kingdom-hearts-announcement-soon/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管《最终幻想 Versus XIII》自2005年11月起就已经开始开发，但直到2011年9月仍旧未进入全力开发阶段<!-- Although development of Final Fantasy Versus XIII started in November 2005, it did not enter 100% production power until September 2011. --><ref>{{cite web|title=Final Fantasy Versus XIII Finally Goes Into Full Production|url=http://www.justpushstart.com/2011/09/11/final-fantasy-versus-xiii-finally-goes-into-full-production/|first=Damian|last=Seeto|publisher=Just Push Start|date=September 11, 2011|language=en|accessdate=2013-10-30|archive-date=2019-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630233846/https://www.justpushstart.com/2011/09/final-fantasy-versus-xiii-finally-goes-into-full-production/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2013年6月的{{tsl|en|E3 2013|E3展会}}上披露，《最终幻想 Versus XIII》已经切换平台至[[遊戲機歷史_(第八世代)|次时代主机]][[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]上，并被更名为《最终幻想XV》<!-- In June 2013 at {{tsl|en|E3 2013}} it was revealed that Final Fantasy Versus XIII had shifted to next gen consoles, the [[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]] and the [[Xbox_One|Xbox One]] and would be rebranded as [[Final_Fantasy_XV|Final Fantasy XV]]. --><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2013/06/final-fantasy-versus-xiii-xv/|title=Final Fantasy Versus XIII Is Now Final Fantasy XV|publisher=Wired.com|author=Chris Kohler|date=2006-10-13|language=en|accessdate=2013-10-24|archive-date=2014-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227075708/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2013/06/final-fantasy-versus-xiii-xv|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2014年9月，史克威尔艾尼克斯宣布野村哲也将不再担任《最终幻想XV》的监制<!--似乎媒体用的都是导演来说这个职位-->，他的职位将由《[[最终幻想_零式|最终幻想 零式]]》的制作人[[田畑端|田畑端]]接替。<ref>[http://game.163.com/14/0918/10/A6DTQJVC00314K8I.html 野村哲也不再继续担任《最终幻想15》的导演] {{Wayback|url=http://game.163.com/14/0918/10/A6DTQJVC00314K8I.html |date=20141222155811 }}.网易游戏.2014-09-18.[2014-12-22].</ref>

=== 2015年後 ===
2015年6月E3展，史克威爾艾尼克斯發表《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》，並宣佈由野村哲也監督，獲得了極大的迴響。<ref>[https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=116710 野村哲也表示《FF VII 重製版》在 PS4 HD 版發表前就已開始製作野村哲也] {{Wayback|url=https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=116710 |date=20190526131848 }}.2015-06-20.</ref>

== 风格 ==

在游戏艺术风格方面，野村认为天野喜孝是给他带来最大影响的人<ref name="FlareG" />。其他四位被他视作带来主要影响的“前辈”还包括[[坂口博信|坂口博信]]、[[北濑佳范|北濑佳范]]、[[伊藤裕之|伊藤裕之]]和[[高橋哲哉_(遊戲製作人)|高桥哲哉]]。在思考关于王国之心的游戏系统创意时，战斗系统设计师伊藤所做的工作给他带来了很大启发。<!-- [[Yoshitaka_Amano|Yoshitaka Amano]] had been considered by Nomura as one of his biggest influences when doing artworks for the games.<ref name="FlareG" /> His four "seniors" that also were major influences include [[Yoshinori_Kitase|Yoshinori Kitase]], [[Hironobu_Sakaguchi|Hironobu Sakaguchi]], {{tsl|en|Hiroyuki Ito}} and [[Tetsuya_Takahashi|Tetsuya Takahashi]]. Ito's work as a battle system designer inspires him when thinking of the gameplay system for the Kingdom Hearts games. --><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_third_party_game_developers_31641_49615.html#top|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120904023724/http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_third_party_game_developers_31641_49615.html%23top#top|archivedate=2012-09-04|title=Iwata asks|publisher=Nintendo|language=en|date=2012-04-03|accessdate=2013-10-30|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。在设计角色时，野村偏向于使角色的名字以及着装与其个性相关联。一个例子是在游戏《最终幻想X》中，对比以往最终幻想系列的角色的喜怒无常，本作男主角{{tsl|en|Tidus}}被赋予了丰富多彩的制服，以反映他的性格开朗。其名也与游戏中另一角色{{link-en|YUNA|Yuna}}相对应，前者在[[沖繩語|沖繩語]]中意为“太阳”，后者意为“夜晚”<ref name="FlareG" />。<!-- When designing characters, Nomura wants their names and outfits be related with their personalities. An example occurs in Final Fantasy X where the protagonist {{tsl|en|Tidus}} was given a colorful uniform in order to reflect his cheerful personality and contrast previous moody Final Fantasy characters. His name is also related with the one from [[Yuna|Yuna]], another character appearing in the game, with the former being for "Sun" and the latter Okinawan for "night".<ref name="FlareG" /> Various characters such as {{tsl|en|Squall Leonheart}} and {{tsl|en|Lulu (Final Fantasy)|Lulu}} are given multiple accessories, making the games more challenging for the programmers.<ref name="FlareG" /> -->

在导演《降临之子》时，野村解释说，由于剧中很多疑团缺乏来自情节的直接答案，本片风格迥异于西方电影。他进一步解释说，希望观众能自己去解读影片中的某些场景，并同自己的朋友们一起讨论这些东西以另一种方式来欣赏这部影片<!-- When directing Advent Children, Nomura explained how the film was different from Western films due to the lack of direct answers from the plot. He added that he wants viewers to interpret certain scenes themselves and then discussing them with friends as another way to enjoy the film. --><ref name="prologue" />。类似的手法也被运用在王国之心系列游戏的场景中，在这些场景中通常会显示一些未知的字符以留给玩家想象空间，直到后续情节才揭露<!-- The same occurs within the Kingdom Hearts series where the scenes that show unknown characters are left to the player's imagination until the following reveals it. --><ref>{{cite book |title=Kingdom Hearts Another Report (Included with the video game Kingdom Hearts II Final Mix) |date=March 2007|isbn=|language = ja | publisher=Square Enix |page=}}</ref>。

